System requirements:
====================

To use this software, your computer must meet the following specifications:

Supported OS's:

RAM;
====

- 1 GB or more
- 2 GB or more (Windows 8 64-bit / Windows 7 64-bit)

3. Screen:
==========

- Screen resolution; 1024x768 pixels or more
- The screen colors, medium (16-bit) or more

Canon EOS DIGITAL Solution Disk from the complete set of cameras Canon EOS. Contains software for viewing, editing, organizing and printing images, as well as control the camera.

The composition of distributions:
=================================

Digital Photo Professional 3.13.10
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

It is recommended to users, mainly images you shoot RAW. Allows you to quickly view, edit, manipulate, and print images RAW. You can also edit images JPEG, keeping the original files.

EOS Utility 2.13.10
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

When the camera is connected to a computer, EOS Utility allows you to transfer photos to a computer and a video shot with the camera. This software can also be used to configure various camera settings and remote shooting by connecting the camera to a computer.

Picture Style Editor 1.13.10
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Allows you to edit image styles, create and save original Picture Style files.


Installation Instructions:
==========================

1. Extract Canon EOS DIGITAL Solution Disk v28.1A ( ksd281a_installer.exe will be extracted by default to your downloads directory. You can change the extraction location if required ).
2. Once extracted, right click on ksd281a_installer,exe and run as administrator.
3. Select your desired language and install.
